Novice.bio: If you prefer cannabis' therapeutic effects -- calming, pain management, anti-anxiety -- more than its heady, trippy aspects, you have many options with products high in CBD and low in THC.
Novice.strains: Restore, BrainPower, Complete in Oils, Extracts, and Capsules

Average.bio: CBD products are organic, natural, and legal to buy in every state. CBD has therapeutic effects -- calming, pain management, anti-anxiety -- and also helps protect against bone loss and osteoporosis.

Sensitive.bio: CBD products can be vaped, mixed with food, swallowed, and even applied topically. A great way to relax is with a tea containing CBD at night time.
Sensitive.strains: Capsules, Extract, topical Shea Butter Creme
